      "value": "<p>Flesh magicians, also known as caromancers, are experts at the destruction, production, and manipulation of flesh and muscles. Their thralls generally take on the form of zombies and other creatures of dead flesh.</p><p><strong>Class Feat</strong> Dead Weight</p><p><strong>General Feat</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.AmP0qu7c5dlBSath]{Toughness}</p><p><strong>Thrall Enhancement</strong> You can still make use of a destroyed thrall's flesh. Whenever one of your thralls is destroyed, you can cause the thrall to leave behind difficult terrain in the space they were destroyed. The difficult terrain lasts for 10 minutes.</p>"
